resolution.summary:
Do not merge until https://github.com/project-radius/radius/pull/1941 is ready.

As we are moving to the bicep extensibility provider and the deployment engine, we need to match the implementation they have for extensibility. Mostly small changes. 

@rynowak the names for extensibility types in arm.json remove the prefix `kubernetes.` from the types: https://github.com/Azure/bicep/blob/95fe13aee76e2f02ee1ffd74a390646f882f4b2a/docs/examples_extensibility/aks/modules/kubernetes.json#L94, I assume we should do the same?
